ong \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng t\u00e2m linh c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t. Mang m\u1ed9t gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb nh\u00e2n v\u0103n s\u00e2u s\u1eafc v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea1o l\u00fd \&quot; U\u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1edb ngu\u1ed3n\&quot;. C\u00f9ng ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ea7y c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 ng\u00e0y l\u1ec5 Vu Lan \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n th\u1eadt c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y nh\u00e9.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/YLiXQyuTj6brtyjWPMKI3T1kEKnaGfyxC8xwzq7JQ0Dnb.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;h2&gt;H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh l\u1ec5 vu lan b\u00e1o hi\u1ebfu cha m\u1eb9 \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u1ea5t 2021&lt;\/h2&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft l\u1ec5 Vu Lan th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y r\u1eb1m th\u00e1ng 7. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y l\u1ec5 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi con Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, ng\u00e0y l\u1ec5 n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c ch\u00f9a. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ph\u1eadt t\u1eed m\u00e0 l\u1ec5 Vu Lan l\u00e0 l\u1ec5 b\u00e1o \u00e2n, b\u00e1o hi\u1ebfu v\u1edbi cha m\u1eb9 m\u00e0 m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi con c\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang ki\u1ebfp n\u00e0y m\u00e0 c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u ki\u1ebfp kh\u00e1c.\u00a0&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Ng\u00e0y l\u1ec5 vu lan nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta s\u1ed1ng ch\u1eadm l\u1ea1i. Ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 cha m\u1eb9 - ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecbu kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i n\u1ea5ng, d\u1ea1y d\u1ed7 ch\u00fang ta n\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi. L\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 ta h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u00e2m l\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh k\u00ednh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9. Nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft \u0111\u00e3 r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng v\u00ec ch\u01b0a k\u1ecbp b\u00e1o hi\u1ebfu th\u00ec b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tr\u00ean c\u00f5i \u0111\u1eddi n\u00e0y. V\u00ec v\u1eady ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ghi nh\u1edb h\u00e3y l\u00e0m b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi h\u1ecd c\u00f2n s\u1ed1ng.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/dq3cCdqAdiYpFUlVG7uIIrGZ2SurE8zcryToLCFR40Uwk.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;V\u00e0 th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb9p thay nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1c \u00fd ngh\u0129a m\u00f9a Vu Lan l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u01b0u gi\u1eef tr\u00ean nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m \u1ea3nh. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng nhau ng\u1eafm qua nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u00fd ngh\u0129a m\u00f9a Vu Lan nh\u00e9.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/WKPkHDY0VGiYkeHckwnhstFRv42dF7XZNSEquQVg1Nvku.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/Q6miicvh8UfDnvb3ohR4PNDvrRC0eol3oPYPX5v2PUhPU.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/g4MzOYv9dyZYJqQUUnvm1aWv5oCKG0We7PadvE6hS0Fxh.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/7qIrUZp45XgJzieo1lBOuuHeQBR1EDEZKfhua8yd76ax7.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/SJDLYtwMT4yJSD8ObC8Ksd3ARmrK8qKTwV1oTgLPNtXXQ.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/yqzcegJPBY1ir2Jok25hNtR59bvtMNRRnbxmMV1ct3uAi.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/AOm0ZA9FVsG00ijxmWLS7JrHLqhYquxWdP0vmsoYfq9iI.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/m89p784AK41oAR7XDAFBHKq3izfVwUtprUNQiPTU9Pgfg.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\u00a0&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc b\u00f4ng h\u1ed3ng c\u00e0i \u00e1o l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0ng tr\u00e1i tim ng\u01b0\u1eddi con lu\u00f4n h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 cha m\u1eb9. C\u00f3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft v\u1ee1 \u00f2a tu\u00f4n r\u01a1i. H\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac c\u00f3, \u0111au bu\u1ed3n c\u00f3, \u00e2n h\u1eadn c\u0169ng c\u00f3. C\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec v\u1eabn c\u00f2n cha m\u1eb9 \u1edf b\u00ean. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft \u0111au bu\u1ed3n \u00e2n h\u1eadn v\u00ec ch\u01b0a k\u1ecbp b\u00e1o hi\u1ebfu cho cha m\u1eb9. C\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng khi\u1ebfn cha m\u1eb9 bu\u1ed3n l\u00f2ng.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/VcneIQpOr3qowf2BMogsuHY9SwnG89eglHqf4QweSuBdW.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/U33X0Yg0an9vl9Q61aBVTsPOepKgyANvOruPx7z4eRfTG.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/pWH2EPg1IYmSrQktXyiXB43XaUtKSfr7NMMF7g65rV40S.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/jvyeZvsTwWz5s6tUKRw7E9HBGWjmOMvxXsn8JvJlAoTqy.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/Cbi9bOZWuhTAk6dDJhPdDZ00zjH1hG4W3pVXZIygLyutH.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;h2&gt;K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn&lt;\/h2&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh vu lan b\u00e1o hi\u1ebfu cha m\u1eb9 c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t 2021. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p n\u00e0y. Ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m h\u00ecnh m\u00ecnh th\u00edch l\u00e0m h\u00ecnh n\u1ec1n \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, laptop, \u0111\u0103ng l\u00ean facebook,..\u0110\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1edb \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp vu lan v\u1ec1. Hay nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m cho b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, c\u1ea7u mong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9. Ch\u00fac b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u1eadt h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y \u00fd ngh\u0129a.\u00a0&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\u00a0&lt;\/p&gt;\n&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m h\u00ecnh ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1ec5 vu lan b\u00e1o hi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1edb \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u00e3y theo d\u00f5i ngay b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m \u1ea3nh c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t nh\u00e9.&quot;,&quot;thumb_image&quot;:null,&quot;tags&quot;:[],&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;tong-hop-hinh-anh-vu-lan-bao-hieu-cha-me-cam-dong-dep-nhat-2021&quot;,&quot;content_share&quot;:null,&quot;image&quot;:&quot;articles\/C11lzJDGuiUslBo87v09mEjRhEIRt8JbMqn7dUiS.jpg&quot;,&quot;like&quot;:0,&quot;love&quot;:0,&quot;ha